
4 layer architecture

UI Layer => is to showcase the UI and  handle Navigation (Component and pages)
Hooks layer => is to manage the state of the application and also to make API calls {/features/auth/hooks/useAuth.js}
state layer => to manage the data store from the backend (store the responses) [auth.context.jsx] {features/auth/auth.context.jsx} createContext and AuthContext
API layer => is use to communicate with backend (services/auth.api.js) {/features/auth/service/auth.api.js}